[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 1.418,
    "text": "Hey!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1.418,
    "endTime": 2.543,
    "text": "Shh, shh, shh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.254,
    "endTime": 6.3389999999999995,
    "text": "Okay, so say hi to my friend and tell him you like my hat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.631,
    "endTime": 8.06,
    "text": "Okay, so, um, what's your friend's name?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.06,
    "endTime": 8.966000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, Chandler."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.3,
    "endTime": 11.011000000000001,
    "text": "So, hi, Chandler."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.344,
    "endTime": 12.761,
    "text": "- That, that was.. - Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.762,
    "endTime": 15.473,
    "text": "- Oh, my God. - That's Fergie, baby!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.975,
    "endTime": 21.061,
    "text": "Joey says you don't really like his hat, but I think it's kinda dashing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.23,
    "endTime": 23.648,
    "text": "When did you? How? How?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.648,
    "endTime": 26.15,
    "text": "Well, I was trying to  figure out how to get to Buckingham Palace, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.15,
    "endTime": 28.528,
    "text": "So, I'm in my map, and-and.."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.195,
    "endTime": 29.654,
    "text": "Hey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.28,
    "endTime": 31.031000000000002,
    "text": "- Hey. - Hey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.906,
    "endTime": 34.117,
    "text": "I understand you had a little talk with Emily."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.117,
    "endTime": 36.244,
    "text": "Yes, I did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.244,
    "endTime": 38.621,
    "text": "And you are welcome."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.665,
    "endTime": 42.0,
    "text": "Am I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.334,
    "endTime": 46.17100000000001,
    "text": "And was it your idea to postpone the wedding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.006,
    "endTime": 48.965,
    "text": "Um..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.174,
    "endTime": 50.842,
    "text": "- I'm gonna go to the bathroom. - Wait up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.428,
    "endTime": 57.265,
    "text": "Hey, hey, since you're the fix-it lady, here's a pickle."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.766,
    "endTime": 62.352,
    "text": "What do you do when the bride says she doesn't wanna have the wedding at all? "
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.687,
    "endTime": 64.521,
    "text": "-She said that? -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.772,
    "endTime": 66.232,
    "text": "-Why? -I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.232,
    "endTime": 71.488,
    "text": "I told her it was stupid to put off the wedding just because the hall was gone, and she, like, flipped out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.405,
    "endTime": 73.531,
    "text": "Oh my God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.99,
    "endTime": 76.533,
    "text": "You're even dumber than I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.035,
    "endTime": 77.786,
    "text": "Excuse me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.12,
    "endTime": 81.456,
    "text": "Ross, how long, have you planning this wedding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.04,
    "endTime": 83.54100000000001,
    "text": "I don't know. A month?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.541,
    "endTime": 86.544,
    "text": "Emily has probably  been planning it since she was five."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.128,
    "endTime": 91.091,
    "text": "Ever since the first time she took a pillowcase and hung it off the back of her head."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.425,
    "endTime": 94.219,
    "text": "That's what we did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.594,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "We dreamed about the perfect wedding..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 101.0,
    "text": "… in the perfect place..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 103.436,
    "text": "… with the perfect four-tiered wedding cake..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.313,
    "endTime": 107.732,
    "text": "… with the little people on top."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.407,
    "endTime": 125.5,
    "text": "But the most important part is that we had the perfect guy who understood just how important all that other stuff was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.919,
    "endTime": 129.838,
    "text": "I had no idea."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.172,
    "endTime": 132.85,
    "text": "And that-that pillowcase thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.85,
    "endTime": 135.29999999999998,
    "text": "I thought you guys were just doing the flying nun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.47,
    "endTime": 139.597,
    "text": "Sometimes we were."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.432,
    "endTime": 142.1,
    "text": "Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.351,
    "endTime": 144.978,
    "text": "You're gonna help me figure out what to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.978,
    "endTime": 147.60500000000002,
    "text": "- All right. - Come on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.484,
    "endTime": 152.77700000000002,
    "text": "Oh, pretty intense, huh?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.777,
    "endTime": 153.611,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.363,
    "endTime": 159.617,
    "text": "Hey, I hope Ross didn't think we just went in there because we were uncomfortable being out here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.082,
    "endTime": 168.126,
    "text": "I hope he did."
  }
]